<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Luiguom thuk-thim leh zanthim takmai achun,
 Gitloh thukpen apat ka tha hung kitin;
 &quot;Kumkhaw hinna vak lam hi hun zuon inla,
 Hun hengilh ngei puong ie&quot; Lal Isu'n Atii.

[V2]
 &quot;Hun hengilh ngei puong ie&quot; (na) damsungin,
 Khut in hun tuzing (ing) ka;
 Ka thupiek haw (hi) sungilh ki'n,
 Hun hengilh (ngei) puong ie, damsung in,
 Na Hukdampa ka hi, hun veng zel ing ka.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel thimna leh meipi'n ei khuh laiin,
 A hehpihna leh lainatna ka hengilh;
 Tuhin Kalvari a hehpihna ka he'i,
 Amah lochuh muonna dang a um puoh ie.

[V4]
 3. Kinem mah mah in Lalpa ka hun zuon hi,
 Nang chawihatna lasa'n na kawm ka hun zuon;
 Leisiet apat Van Lal Cha hizaw dingin,
 Isu'n eisam zing hi, A Van In akhun.

[V5]
 4. Van mun lopi Sana khawpi enzing in,
 Lungzin lungdawnna hungtung zing mahlele;
 Vangphatna go leh chawlhdamna chuh mu'n la,
 Na kumsawt mun lam chuh enzing zieng maiin.</lyrics>
<title>I WILL NOT FORGET THEE</title>
</song>